.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, disaster, horror, romance
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, milk, soy-milk, cola
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, rowing, tennis, water-polo
1. the person drinking cola is in an even position##4
2. the person watching disaster movies is the person who's sport is rowing##1
3. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
4. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies##3
5. the person drinking cola is the person who's sport is badminton##1
6. the person watching horror movies is the person drinking coffee##1
7. the person drinking soy-milk is the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | crime  | romance   | horror     | disaster |
| Beverage   | soy-milk  | cola      | coffee        | milk     |
| Sport         | tennis | badminton | water-polo | rowing   |

