.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-6::.
There 4 different types of food: apricot, kiwi, lemon, pepper
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, fishing, sudoku, woodworking
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, soul, pop, techno
1. the person eating kiwi is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of pop is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
3. the fan of jazz is the person eating kiwi##1
4. the person eating lemon is on the left of the fan of soul##1
5. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far right##1
6. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person eating kiwi##1
7. the person eating pepper is in an even position##4
8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4    |
| Food    | lemon   | pepper      | kiwi       | apricot |
| Hobby   | camping | woodworking | sudoku     | fishing |
| Music-Genre     | techno     | soul  | jazz | pop |

