.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-7::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, cricket, rowing, sailing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, martial-arts, satire, time-travel
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goat, guinea-pig, horse
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person watching comedy movies##1
2. the owner of the goat is between the person watching time-travel movies and the owner of the chinchilla##2
3. the person watching time-travel movies is the person who's sport is cricket##1
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3
5. the person who's sport is surfing is in an even position##4
6. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
7. the person watching comedy movies is the person who's sport is surfing##1
8. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |       3       |     4      |
| Sport      | rowing   | sailing          | cricket | surfing        |
| Movie-Genre   | satire     | martial-arts | time-travel   | comedy     |
| Pet           | chinchilla | goat         | horse         | guinea-pig |

