.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-8::.
4 different games are played: bridge, scrabble, snooker, mah-jongg
The people have 4 different jobs:  journalist, librarian, scientist, social-worker
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, disco, electronic, house
1. the fan of house is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
2. the scientist is the person playing bridge##1
3. the social-worker is the person playing snooker##1
4. the person playing snooker is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
5. the fan of disco is between the journalist and the person playing bridge##2
6. the fan of house is on the left or right of the scientist##3
7. the person playing bridge is in an even position##4
8. the person playing bridge is between the person playing scrabble and the person playing snooker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Game         | scrabble | bridge      | snooker       | mah-jongg    |
| Job           | librarian  | scientist  | social-worker | journalist |
| Music-Genre   | house      | electronic | disco         | country    |

