.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-9::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta, iced-tea, water
The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, manager, pilot, social-worker
City: prague, paris, colone, rome
1. the entrepreneur is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
3. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
4. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
5. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person traveling to colone##3
6. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
7. the entrepreneur is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
8. the manager is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
9. the social-worker is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |      3       |       4       |
| Beverage   | fanta         | coffee  | iced-tea     | water         |
| Job        | social-worker | manager | entrepreneur | pilot         |
| City      | paris         | colone  | prague   | rome |

