.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-12::.
There 4 different types of food: avocado, cherry, lime, peach
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, tulip, poppy, zinnia
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, dubstep, jazz, r&b
1. the person eating cherry is on the left of the person eating peach##1
2. the person eating lime is on the far left##1
3. the fan of dubstep is on the left or right of the fan of r&b##3
4. the person eating lime is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
5. the fan of d&b is between the person who growszinnia and the fan of r&b##2
6. the person who growspoppy is in an even position##4
7. the person eating avocado is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | lime    | cherry  | peach  | avocado |
| Flower   | zinnia | tulip | marigold | poppy |
| Music-Genre   | jazz    | d&b     | r&b    | dubstep |

