The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, mystery, satire, superhero
City: boston, marseilles, nizza, hamburg
1. the person traveling to marseilles is in an even position##4
2. the person traveling to marseilles is the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
4. the person drinking cola is the person watching superhero movies##1
5. the person drinking cola is on the far left##1
6. the person watching family movies is the person traveling to marseilles##1
7. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
8. the person traveling to hamburg is the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |   4    |
| Beverage      | cola      | almond-milk | 7up     | tea    |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | family      | mystery | satire |
| City           | nizza   | marseilles  | boston     | hamburg |

