5. the person playing snooker is the canadian##1
6. the fan of indie is on the right of the french##1
7. the french is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
8. the fan of d&b is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3     |    4     |
| Game   | scrabble | monopoly | snooker | domino   |
